text:
There are four dead documentation links on the ASF/JMeter page, under the heading "Tutorials (PDF)", 
e.g.,

http://jakarta.apache.org/usermanual/jmeter_distributed_testing_step_by_step.pdf

I believe these can all be corrected by inserting "jmeter/" into the URL, e.g.,

http://jakarta.apache.org/jmeter/usermanual/jmeter_distributed_testing_step_by_step.pdf
creator: blenko@martingalesystems.com
